text: Kamila Dubcová (born 17 January 1999) is a Czech footballer who plays as a midfielder for Sassuolo and has appeared for the Czech Republic women's national team. ==Career== Dubcová has been capped for the Czech Republic national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Czech women's footballers Category:Czech Republic women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:1.
